t: "It is up to you ňĻO Prophetňļ to delay or receive whoever you please of your wives. There is no blame on you if you call back any of those you have set aside.¬†That is more likely that they will be content, not grieved, and satisfied with what you offer them all. Allah ňĻfullyňļ knows what is in your hearts. And Allah is All-Knowing, Most Forbearing"